  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Back Market maintains strict guidelines on sellable items to ensure quality, safety, and customer satisfaction. This article outlines which items are prohibited or restricted on our platform.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Prohibited Items</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>The following items are not allowed on Back Market for reasons including reliability, compatibility, customer experience, or market value:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Non-electronic items or items not considered electronic accessories</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Health-related devices (reliability cannot be fully guaranteed)</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Devices with unsupported or unupgradable operating systems, as they cannot deliver a reliable, up-to-date user experience</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Devices with high return rates or persistent issues (e.g., certain LG devices)</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Items priced above market value (including shipping, e.g., old video games)</span></li></ul>\n<p><br><img src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0aT000000NkRx&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb00000IhEoY\" alt=\"\" width=\"820\" height=\"413\"></img> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>For the full, most up-to-date list, please refer to the attached document.</em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The latest updates to this list include mostly devices that are too obsolete to function well or products with characteristics that could mislead customers or be perceived as counterfeit, such as:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">iPad mini 2s and mini 3s</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">All brands of Apple-like earphones </span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Wired earphones with lightning connectors</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Low performing Desktops and the ones that do not support Windows 10.</span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Restricted categories of items that require approval</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Some categories are restricted due to quality and/or legal concerns. Only sellers who have completed a specific approval process can list the products in these categories.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><br><strong>To access the restricted category</strong>, you need to submit a request through the Seller Support Center and provide, depending on the category you’re applying for: photos of the devices, samples to the lab for testing, testing reports, and invoices proving your sourcing. <br>Only a limited number of sellers are selected for <strong>strategic partnerships</strong>. We require a proven quality track record and reliable sourcing. Please reach out to your dedicated point of contact for more information.<br></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/How-do-I-get-approved-to-sell-in-restricted-categories\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\">More details are available here</a></span><br>For questions, contact your Back Market representative. Once you are ready, submit your request via the Seller Support Center.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Note: </strong>Sellers in onboarding or launch phases are not eligible to sell in these categories.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"width: 100.059%;border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Restricted categories</span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Categories limited to strategic partnerships</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Apple earphones (AirPods)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Brand New smartphone accessories (Cases, tempered glass screen protectors, smartphone chargers)</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Apple Pencil</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Gaming PCs</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">AirTag</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Well-Known brand items like Dyson, Devialet, etc.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">MacBook chargers</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Computer hardware (graphic cards)</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Cases with keyboard</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Computer chargers</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Cases and protections for Airpods</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Apple-branded cables</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Cases and protections for Laptops</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Apple-original cases</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Cases and protection for Airtags</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">External batteries</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Cases and protections for Apple Watch</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Obsolete Laptops</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Tablet cases and protections</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Christmas Boxes and other limited editions</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Old school mobile phones</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Watches (without band)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 28.155%;border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Apple Watches (without band)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 71.938%;border-color: #000000;\"></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Requiring special attention</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Apple Earphones: Special Restrictions prior to approval</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Due to a high risk of counterfeiting, to apply for Apple Earphones you must:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Have total sales of at least €650,000 in the 90 days before your application</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Have been actively selling on Back Market for over 6 months</span></li></ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>MacBook Chargers and Apple earphones: Special restriction post-approval</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You must reach at least €5,000 GMV (Gross Merchandise Volume) in the category within 90 days</span></li><li style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">No counterfeit alerts in the last quarter (for any device)</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Failure to meet these criteria will lead to deactivation of your selling privileges in the approved category.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Safety Compliance</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">For hazardous items (like chargers), <span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/Charger-compliance-with-International-Safety-Standard-IEC-62368-1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #2980b9;\">you must comply with safety regulations</a></span>. For cables, you are required to provide an Underwriter Laboratories (UL) certification or equivalent within 5 business days upon request.</span></p>"
}